articles.author: Clarissa Brincat
articles.title: Never-before-seen cells unveiled in detailed map of developing human heart - Livescience.com
articles.description: The most comprehensive cell "atlas" of the developing human heart to date was crafted using cutting-edge technology and includes never-before-seen cell types.
articles.content:
Scientists just published the most detailed map of the developing human heart to date.
